layout.p:
Columns: 1 2;
                                                  ruled lines: 5 45;
                                                  written lines: 5 45; Uniform layout. Blank pages (e.g., folios 2v, 3r), erasures (e.g., folios 56r, 72v, 101v, 102r). Ruling is sometimes visible. Flesh side and hair side are distinguishable. Hebrew foliation from folio 12r. Numerous marginal notes.
Several folios, entire quires are missing; paper leaves, quires added later to fill the numerous lacunae. The lack is reflected sometimes on the Hebrew foliation and quire numbering (e. g. between ff. 350 and 351). Incomplete at the end. Watermark, folio 7 (paper leaf), unidentified.
